{"tid":2266693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中美兩軍視像對話 促溝通化危機","createTime":"2020-11-01T13:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T13:31:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a25239a079a62b2f7723f2222a1ded5a072e83f","tid":2266693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/53D2VJ6QWNDFFJ7SWA4QKZERKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2F53D2VJ6QWNDFFJ7SWA4QKZERKQ%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=2756fdb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2F53D2VJ6QWNDFFJ7SWA4QKZERKQ%2F&h=27df6872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/53D2VJ6QWNDFFJ7SWA4QKZERKQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中美兩軍視像對話 促溝通化危機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pELacfV9pQliV5MIN0A_UyEkgos=/1187x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IAL4CXVA5VA4TAKBQGTTZAESWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpELacfV9pQliV5MIN0A_UyEkgos%3D%2F1187x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIAL4CXVA5VA4TAKBQGTTZAESWA.jpg&h=7dc35512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國大選舉行前夕，中美兩軍日前舉行了一連兩天的「危機溝通工作組」視訊會議，並已商議在本年內再舉行另外兩場視像會議。正在進行南亞及東南亞五國訪問的美國國務卿蓬佩奧，昨在行程最後一站越南強調美方對越南的主權懷有「崇高敬意」，被指力挺越南在南海主權爭議問題上對抗中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧挺越擁南海主權<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部發言人吳謙（圖）前天在記者會上表示，中美兩軍近期進行了多項交流，包括10月20日中央軍委國際軍事合作辦公室領導與美國防部高層官員通電話，本周三和四（28日至29日）舉行了危機溝通工作組視訊會議。他謂。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧從印尼轉抵越南訪問，在與總理阮春福會面後稱：「我們盼望一起致力共建兩國關係，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，德國國防部長凱倫鮑爾昨狠批中國的國家資本主義對歐盟和美國都「具攻擊性」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中新社/路透社"}]}